```plantuml
@startuml pgrignaffini_AlgoCrowd

skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor LightSkyBlue
  BorderColor Black
  ArrowColor Black
}

[Next.js Frontend] as Frontend
[Express.js Backend] as Backend
[SQLite Database] as DB
[Algorand Blockchain] as Blockchain
[PyTeal Smart Contracts] as SmartContracts

package "Frontend Components" {
  [Pages]
  [React Components]
  [API Functions]
  [AppContext]
  [Utility Functions]
}

package "Backend Components" {
  [REST API Endpoints]
  [Database Access Object]
}

Frontend --> Backend : HTTP Requests
Backend --> DB : SQL Queries
Backend --> Blockchain : Interact
Frontend --> Blockchain : Interact via AlgoSigner
SmartContracts --> Blockchain : Deploy

Frontend ..> [Pages]
Frontend ..> [React Components]
Frontend ..> [API Functions]
Frontend ..> [AppContext]
Frontend ..> [Utility Functions]

Backend ..> [REST API Endpoints]
Backend ..> [Database Access Object]

note right of Frontend
  Decentralized crowdfunding platform
  built on Algorand blockchain
end note

note right of SmartContracts
  Govern funding, refunds,
  and fund collection
end note

@enduml
```